metadata.description:
This NFT grants a Lifetime Membership Pass to CUBAN'S EDGE. 
The NFT and soundscape were designed and handcrafted by multi award-winning VR and 3D artist Ratbag (https://twitter.com/ratbag_gif). 
The NFT provides access to the CUBAN'S EDGE trading suite and Discord; which includes over 20+ specialized trading tools and indicators. 
Including on-chain wallet tracking of over 500+ of the top trading firms, traders, and influencers, plus public crypto project Github tracking, macroeconomic calendar with live data, and market-wide alerts for all of the favorite tools. 
For more information and access instructions, head to https://www.cubansedge.com/
metadata.name: Lifetime Membership Pass
